# Styling and i18n

- Prefer `className` with NativeWind utilities.
- Use NativeWind theme tokens/classes instead of hardcoded hex values.
- Use `style` only for truly dynamic or computed values.
- Keep user-facing text translated via i18next keys.
- Default assumptions should support Romanian fallback behavior.

## Avoid

- Hardcoded UI labels/messages in JSX.
- Hardcoded color literals when token equivalents exist.
